overview: The user was experiencing deployment failures caused by several
  linting issues. I systematically addressed these by adding missing curly
  braces in src/lib/auth.ts, removing an unused ADMIN_PASSWORD variable from
  src/middleware.ts, and refactoring fetchResponses with useCallback in
  src/app/admin/AdminDashboardClient.tsx to resolve a useEffect dependency
  warning. After fixing the linting errors, the build process revealed a new
  type error in prisma.config.ts related to an incompatible resolveAdapter API
  and a version mismatch between Prisma and its adapter. I determined this file
  was redundant as the adapter was already configured in src/lib/prisma.ts and
  proceeded to delete it. However, the file seemed to persist or regenerate,
  indicating a deeper issue that requires further investigation.
